nodes.title: Subject #2 -
widgets_values: Majestic pool lifeguard on duty embedding:dr-strange

Black Reroute nodes are switches. There are 4 distinct switches present:
  1) unCLIP On/Off (1 for background & 1 per subject) - for 'on' connect unCLIPConditioning
  2) ControlNet (1 for background & 1 per subject) - for 'on' connect ControlNetApply
  3) Model Upscale/Latent Upscale (in Upscale) - chose upscaling method
  4) Upscale Result/Don't Upscale (in Upscale Result)- whether to upscale the image after the second pass again or not

Stable Diffusion only supports resolutions that are multiples of 64. Keep that in mind when setting Upscale Multiplier in Loaders/Settings to non-integer values, especially when working with multiple subjects
Upscale Multiplier in the Upscale Result group can be set to anything

For single subject use only Background group

The grid size for this workflow is 25
